[[Category:Dutch conjunctions]]
[[Category:Dutch adverbs]]
===Adverb===
'''wanneer'''
# [[when]]
#: ''Wanneer komt de trein?'' &mdash; When does the train arrive?

====Derived terms====
* [[wanneer dan ook]]

===Conjunction===
'''wanneer'''
# [[when]]
#: ''Wanneer ik dat doe, gebeurt er dit.'' &mdash; When I do that, this happens.
# [[if]]
#: ''Het zou lukken wanneer je meer je best deed.'' &mdash; You would succeed if you worked harder.
# [[whenever]], [[if]]
#: ''Wanneer hij mij ziet, loopt hij weg.'' &mdash; Whenever he sees me, he runs away.

